{"tid":2497031,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"馬斯克：特斯拉德州致命車禍無關Autopilot或FSD自駕系統","createTime":"2021-04-20T08:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T08:48:24.000Z","uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7978c107b22d53a939bc08ad81a42d95478fa765","tid":2497031,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:38:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1384254194975010826\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1384254194975010826&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=a775ee4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1384254194975010826&h=97a545fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1384254194975010826</a><br />\n<br />\n美國德州上周六發生特斯拉 (TSLA-US)Model S 衝撞路樹奪走兩命的事故，警方透露事發時駕駛座無人操控，引來兩大交通主管機關調查。執行長馬斯克周一 (19 日) 在推特發文澄清事故無關自駕系統，該車並未啟動 Autopilot 自動輔助駕駛系統，車主也未購買全自動駕駛 (FSD)，特斯拉盤後股價回升。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克表示，根據特斯拉「目前為止」所取得的車輛紀錄，事發當時，該輛車並未啟動 Autopilot，車主也未購買 FSD 系統回升，而且標準的 Autopilot 需要車道線才能啟動，但事故地點沒有清楚的車道線。<br />\n<br />\n他的推文似乎意在回應上周六發生在休士頓附近的致命車禍。根據德州員警說法，警方撲滅火勢後發現車內兩人分別坐在副駕和後座，駕駛座無人，但還無法確定發生事故當下，電動車是否啟動無人駕駛功能。美國高速公路交通安全局 (NHTSA) 和美國國家運輸安全委員會 (NTSB) 兩大主管機關已展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克的談話帶動特斯拉股價盤後回升近 1%。稍早自駕系統疑似釀禍的消息曾使特斯拉一度重挫 6.5%，收盤仍跌 3.4% 至每股 714.63 美元，並拖累美股四大指數皆墨。"},{"pid":"19448bcae06da9db6930d1cb19841648be951099","tid":2497031,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:38:50.000Z","msg":"癲"},{"pid":"602b417279140676be577e3ce09a93fa4d1e5b11","tid":2497031,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:39:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4631546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4631546&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=54b6d272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4631546</a>"},{"pid":"6fb9ecbfb13ed547c508eaca4fcdf5d18e4450df","tid":2497031,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:39:58.000Z","msg":"無自動駕駛 司機位又無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7dec4c62a76e95512598a24ea2ee4db9577fa4","tid":2497031,"uid":64005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:40:37.000Z","msg":"真 用家問題"},{"pid":"2c802f338d2d6568462b2dc22e597b65e667481e","tid":2497031,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fb9ecbfb13ed547c508eaca4fcdf5d18e4450df","tid":2497031,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:39:58.000Z","msg":"無自動駕駛 司機位又無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:44:14.000Z","msg":"撞鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b32696cca258acebf0ad63b6b6d8e50826c3e25","tid":2497031,"uid":329524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:44:27.000Z","msg":"the drive hit and run"},{"pid":"1e47c354907c90040bc4c8035c2ea3257bc86617","tid":2497031,"uid":91604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fb9ecbfb13ed547c508eaca4fcdf5d18e4450df","tid":2497031,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:39:58.000Z","msg":"無自動駕駛 司機位又無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:44:52.000Z","msg":"司機撞左車之後走佬？"},{"pid":"0e5c2fb4953e96b87efb2783ca7486ad647be865","tid":2497031,"uid":4308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自動駕駛系統破解版"}]}